*.spec
# ... but our hand-authored, checked-in build spec IS tracked (the release CI
# runs `pyinstaller packaging/gleplot.spec`; without this negation the *.spec
# rule above silently kept it out of the repo, so CI builds could never start).
!packaging/gleplot.spec

